'''Arkudan gaming cubes''' were fluffy objects purported to bring luck to the owner. [[Tionne Solusar]] hung a pair of centuries old gaming cubes in the cockpit of her ship, the ''[[Lore Seeker]]''.

{{Tech-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
